metadata.name: Moving with Olympus
metadata.description: The Moving with Olympus is the limited NFT series that marks the beginning of a new chapter. The chapter 3,3. This NFT can only be minted within a 3-hour slot. Three hours is all it takes to become a part of something bigger than any one of us. This NFT gives the owner a right to a unique avatar on Mover. Wear the badge of honor.
